graph TD
    %% User Interaction
    User([User]) -->|Chat/Upload| UI[Streamlit UI]
    UI -->|HTTP Requests| API[FastAPI Backend]

    %% Backend Services Layer
    subgraph Backend Services
        API -->|Create Agent| Agent[Talent Matching Agent]
        API -->|Evaluate Response| Evaluator[Evaluation Service]
        API -->|Process CV| Indexer[CV Indexing Service]
    end

    %% Agent logic and Tools
    subgraph Agentic Workflow
        Agent -->|Reasoning| LLM["LLM Provider (Ollama/OpenAI)"]
        Agent -->|Search Candidates| Qdrant[("Qdrant Vector DB")]
        Agent -->|Find Jobs| Ciklum[Ciklum Career Portal]
        Agent -->|Find Jobs| LinkedIn[LinkedIn Search]
        Agent -->|Publish Post| Publisher[LinkedIn API]
    end

    %% Evaluation Logic
    subgraph Evaluation
        Evaluator -->|Judge Response| LLM_Judge[Evaluation LLM]
        LLM_Judge -.->|Relevance, Clarity, Accuracy| UI
    end

    %% Ingestion Pipeline
    subgraph Ingestion Pipeline
        Indexer -->|Extract Text| PDF[PDF Processor]
        PDF -->|Chunk & Embed| Embedder[Semantic Embedder]
        Embedder -->|Store Vectors| Qdrant
    end

    %% Styles
    style User fill:#f9f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style UI fill:#bbf,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style API fill:#dfd,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Agent fill:#fdd,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Qdrant fill:#ff9,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style LLM fill:#eef,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
